President John Magufuli has today appointed Dr Maduhu Kazi the Executive Director of the Tanzania Investment Centre (TIC).

A statement released today on Sunday, July 12, signed by the director of presidential communications Gerson Msigwa says his appointment takes effect from today. Prior to his appointment, Dr Kazi was the manager in the department of budgetary policies and debts at the Bank of Tanzania (BoT). Dr Kazi is replacing Mr Geoffrey Idelphonce Mwambe. 